QuestData.Title: Defend the Gates!
QuestData.Description: Egah - what's going on?$B$B<Screams, shouts, and the roar of combat fills the radio.>$B$B$n! Get back here right away. Hurry back to the gates - we're under attack!$B$BHelp us fend off the invaders. I'm arming your grenade launcher!!
QuestData.LogDescription: Labor Captain Grabbit needs you to rush back to the Rear Gate of Orgrimmar to slay 20 Night Elf Raiders.
QuestData.RewardText: Nice kills, $n - They've never dealt with the likes of you!
